text: Laura Elena, Countess von Bismarck-Schönhausen (née Martínez-Herring; March 3, 1964), commonly known as Laura Harring, is a Mexican-American actress and model. In 1985, Harring became the first Hispanic woman crowned Miss USA. She is best known for her roles as Rita and Camilla Rhodes in the 2001 movie Mulholland Drive. ==References== Category:1964 births Category:Living people Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:American stage actors Category:American voice actors Category:Mexican movie actors Category:Mexican television actors Category:Mexican stage actors Category:Mexican voice actors Category:Mexican models Category:Models from Texas Category:Actors from San Antonio, Texas Category:Miss America winners Category:Miss USA
